# Copy to `.env.legal-notice.de` at the repository root (gitignored).
# Build injects `VITE_LEGAL_NOTICE_DE` via `load-vite-env.mjs`.
#
# Migration: if you used `.env.imprint` with a single `VITE_IMPRINT`, move that German
# statutory text here as `VITE_LEGAL_NOTICE_DE`.

# Plain text. Use \n for line breaks, or double-quoted multiline (dotenv).
# VITE_LEGAL_NOTICE_DE=Angaben gemäß § 5 TMG:\n\nMax Mustermann\nMusterstraße 1\n12345 Musterstadt\n\nKontakt: mail@example.com

VITE_LEGAL_NOTICE_DE="Impressum (Beispiel — in lokaler .env.legal-notice.de ersetzen)\n\nAnbieter: …\nAnschrift: …\nKontakt: …"
